        {
            "title": "屯門藍地毆劫案警拘3男  其中一人涉「搶劫」 今日提堂",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bfc3c77eebeeeac363654f9cd383df4f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250207/_2025020704235317700.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>屯門藍地亦園村初七（4日）發生搶劫案，一名姓蘇男子報稱遭十多名大漢圍毆，混亂間被搶去一條金手鏈、一條金頸鏈及兩部手機，約值13萬元。屯門警區重案組人員經深入調查後，5日拘捕其中三名疑犯。\n\n</p>\n<p>警表示，2月5日在屯門一酒店以涉嫌「搶劫」拘捕3名年齡介乎50至52歲本地男子。其中一名52歲本地男子已被暫控一項「搶劫」罪，案件將於今日（7日）上午在屯門裁判法院提堂。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2051301/即時-港聞-屯門藍地毆劫案警拘3男-其中一人涉-搶劫-今日提堂",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-07 04:31:04",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "天文台：強烈季候風影響  今晚市區最低13度  新界再低一兩度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/df21d6bcf294a593fbbbf58585fa0b49/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250207/_2025020703541023817.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>天文台於今日（7日）凌晨零時零分發出特別天氣提示， 指一股強烈冬季季候風會在今早逐漸影響華南沿岸，本港今日稍後氣溫將逐步下降，天文台屆時會發出寒冷天氣警告。\n\n</p>\n<p>天文台又指，預料明日（8日）早上市區氣溫會在11度左右，渣打馬拉松舉行的星期日（9日）進一步下降至9至10度水平，有機會是入冬以來的最低紀錄。\n\n</p>\n<p>週末期間新界多處地區早上嚴寒，高地氣溫或接近冰點，漸轉天晴及非常乾燥。\n\n</p>\n<p>天文台預測，本港今日大致多雲。早上清涼及有一兩陣微雨，氣溫約15度。日間短暫時間有陽光及乾燥，最高氣溫約18度。稍後氣溫逐步下降，晚上市區最低氣溫約13度，新界再低一兩度。吹和緩東北風，北風逐漸增強。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2051300/即時-港聞-天文台-強烈季候風影響-今晚市區最低13度-新界再低一兩度",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-07 04:01:03",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "上水金舖劫案再拘一29歲非華裔漢  今日提堂",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c02838609c8587448ca5c2df77dd0e26/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250207/_2025020703151039942.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>上水新豐路「南豐珠寶」上月15日傍晚遭多名賊人持刀錘闖入，劫走一批金器首飾，警方翌日拘捕其中一名23歲巴籍疑匪，起回10件手鈪及金鏈。今日（7日）凌晨警方表示，於5日在旺角區再拘捕一名29歲涉案非華裔男子。\n\n</p>\n<p>上月15日，四名身高約一點七米、身穿深色衣服的非華裔男子，以鐵槌敲碎上水新豐路「南豐珠寶」的玻璃櫥窗，並以刀指嚇店員，劫去價值超過一百五十萬元的首飾及金器，其後登上賊車逃去。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4020043/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"4名身穿黑衫的賊人闖入珠寶店，用硬物毀壞多個飾櫃，擸走一批金器首飾。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e1ad735f63877365c63baec0f1f02016/2025-01/8718814901579484_HD_mp4_snapshot_00_00_624.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        4名身穿黑衫的賊人闖入珠寶店，用硬物毀壞多個飾櫃，擸走一批金器首飾。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4020490/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"賊人先後登上一輛接應的私家車。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/31b882fa7ddeea6f5f4a8d90a293ebd7/2025-01/2124016508053354_HD_mp4_snapshot_00_02_282.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        賊人先後登上一輛接應的私家車。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4020491/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名身穿黑色衫白色長褲的賊人「包尾」，差點未能登上賊車離開。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a72faf0a46e9c2f09a8a1e18151f47b6/2025-01/2124016508053354_HD_mp4_snapshot_00_09_836.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名身穿黑色衫白色長褲的賊人「包尾」，差點未能登上賊車離開。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4020319/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"珠寶店內一片狼籍，近門口位置的飾櫃被推翻，玻璃碎裂。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/32e9442ee71c7d829f4013a6b28a7810/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250115_201900649_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        珠寶店內一片狼籍，近門口位置的飾櫃被推翻，玻璃碎裂。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4020320/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大量金器散落地上。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5552da824531a0f42d2070b438ef1739/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250115_201900649_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大量金器散落地上。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4020442/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場位於大埔梧桐寨迴旋處。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ccf7b59ca6c9af88734cab9fb2a547ce/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250115_220719377_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場位於大埔梧桐寨迴旋處。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4020441/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方派出無人機，並配合熱能探測及射燈系統，尋找賊人可能匿藏的位置。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4a0f1950f8429c7d7cb2c39d0768f771/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250115_220719377_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方派出無人機，並配合熱能探測及射燈系統，尋找賊人可能匿藏的位置。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4022024/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方展示證物。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ba055fd852a118f77bba471a1095d56e/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250116_155847602_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方展示證物。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4022023/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方展示證物。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ab87d2e8ba4e201a0f7ad99d13d552a8/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250116_155847602_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方展示證物。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4022021/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方展示證物。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1e0225b8586da7e0f1f8bee7ddc20a7c/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250116_155847602.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方展示證物。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>賊車駛至距離案發現場約11公里的林錦公路迴旋處失事，與另一輛私家車相撞，各匪徒隨即下車後往山坡逃去。警方在賊車上檢獲兩把刀、一個鐵槌及一些懷疑犯人在犯案時所穿着的衣物，並根據情報鎖定匪徒藏身的地點，是距離車禍現場約1.8公里的一間石屋。\n\n</p><h4>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/breaking-news/3420176/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E9%87%91%E8%88%96%E5%8A%AB%E6%A1%884%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E8%B3%8A%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E9%8C%98%E7%8A%AF%E6%A1%88-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%B7%B4%E7%B1%8D%E5%8C%AA%E5%85%AB%E9%84%89%E8%90%BD%E7%B6%B2\" target=\"_blank\">上水金舖劫案｜4黑衣賊持刀錘犯案 消息：一巴籍匪八鄉落網</a></h4>\n<p>16日凌晨約二時，警方在石屋內一名23歲巴籍男子，憑他的衣着相信是閉路電視拍攝到手持鐵錘的劫匪，控以「行劫」罪。人員在現場地上檢獲5條被劫走的金鏈，亦在山邊起回5隻金手鈪。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方今日凌晨表示，新界北總區重案組人員經深入調查後，於今月5日在旺角區拘捕多一名29歲非華裔男子，暫控一項「搶劫」罪，案件將於今日（7日）在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
